r&gt;(Johan Rockström, Ottmar Edenhofer)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + nature_intrinsic_value + climate_tipping_points&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Climate change is a civilizational-scale welfare loss, not a marginal externality: Bressler&#x27;s mortality cost of carbon (~1 death per 4,434 tCO2), PIK&#x27;s committed ~19% income loss by 2049 (Kotz, Levermann &amp; Wenz), and Rockström / Armstrong McKay tipping-element cascades amplifying both. Advocacy that cheaply averts emissions (Clean Air Task Force) enters the slate; where the chain also holds nature&#x27;s intrinsic value, protecting tropical forest — itself a tipping element — picks up the co-benefit. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6unbUdWX67mwXSPKZFkzZIUxSDpkhpiba5kUQtKcd1O53fvoekZMu1sjWQL60jkeee%2B75X3w9CPmWLKDuVIT8YHxwd0fHxMd0qJhLKJAWKfVvhxzKhu4Xvtbu0lCoKHwVf0rJ979937rtU05lMqVs3V%2B8SQJxovYjTTMiEgjmQxuRRypQM5oJFBqg98qlNU6bu2ZKt7ueLmCW6eOETS0TMIn2vZcyXc5YVbzqUsGyh%2BL1IMiUSLYL7RxYtePG%2BS0GEmxm%2Fz0SaimR2n0oc1ZbUOQvmxDbMhCZG16tsjt9TEXGCxpvX%2BogyI5mFoW6Q4jCTSLgmqSyY4k0oxGKecSU0nmdz7nT9h6bpIgksxgsKZJxKDSabA7ibhByIeCQcNZ2xJGSRTDjF8EPUoi9rM58%2FfjFUzXX%2BNeVBhotOaTm1CBuPtCzYS64zmixWtDBizEXNy4qN6RZYr4zJOV1yNltwd%2FH387fnNye352c0WdGMJ1zBkq10VXiehyLbstAhXjYokZnjYYwIJIv1IQm4yoy2sVTw%2BdpY2p11lmBpGgmuW%2FR%2BFbciOUukgt9r39Neg9JR70fdYllHjbzf6PT1C3tywjPmnqZKTthERCIDkYk0GocmbD95DWp%2FbtEFCzIJmUxxB4UDqTF%2FkjVIS%2BImJqSawWnnn5ZnJ5d%2FHP3tM014JJeITnPXOpd%2Fxe9ohevAhkEtFmSHiyBzboDjOEIY6rsI%2FQh3rq65egWHQTgd76qIpGh5bavomPwfdSKAWg5N%2Ft%2BFgI%2FBklK4cJ6DQGJmA2AMoyfNmKkHnoGc0BmHvZsuLI7o4%2B01TSXuwTQZg6aBTB7hDmcbK4JqgZJaNwNgP%2BA5PK74I4fMkHjyKJRMYohnUTOWj9z8JM0CJaYi4PAK0BFlty7JTuUEwTJFcFRqWajYzVXMUxSkmsU9ZOBaN8qUTEWAmHFCxnQSs284EQo%2BYcGDc3ye38QjS846k60NhdohTQrotTAUi4ViMNJdkj86cw66DaT%2FpHc8P%2BeO31sesm7JTt%2F5kOUsO6aXYKsjPEfE