k lives-eq/$1k · 70% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Wild insects (humane pesticides) · 30%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + nature_intrinsic_value + climate_tipping_points + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtz27gV%2FSt3PN1WSi2Zot5O0xnHj00mduJxvPXsxBkFIiEJNUmwAGlFyWZ%2Few8AUqJiuWHqD8nQJHDuue8L6OteyGcsj7JjGfK9w72DA3rx4gVdKyYSyiQFin1Z4WGZ0G3ue50eLaWKwnvBl7TsTPxJd9KbDCcjauhMpjRqmu23CWCOtM7jNBMyoWABtEPyKGVKBgvBIgPWGfvUoRlTE7Zkq8kij1miyw8%2BsUTELNITLWO%2BXLCs%2FNKlhGW54hORZEokWgSTexblvPzeoyDCzoxPMpGmIplPUomla%2BThGhmLMg7pk0iu0Uek89mMK7NvJoNc89Bqc8qCBbGNSkITo8tVtsDzTEScYK7NZ31AmaHMwlDvk%2BKwsUi4JqksmOItWILFHOKFxvtswZ2R%2FqZplieBxXhOgYxTqUFlswB7k5ADEa%2BEtmg6Y0nIIplwiuHEqE2f1j46vf9kqJrt%2FHPKgwwbnbXkzCJs3Nm2YC%2B5zmiaryg3YsxGzauKHdL7hRJxSjc8gus4XSr5b%2BC63b%2Bevj29Oro%2BPaHpiuY84Qp%2BaKerMnZ4KLItMz3Dx31KYH9LxlgSSBbrtyTgKjMqx1IhYtYW026tMwdL00hw3ab3q7gdyXkiFXzb%2BJr29ykd9781LZb11tj7hY5fP7crpzxj7m2q5JRNRSQyEJlKo3ZoAv%2BDt0%2Bdj206Y0EmIRO6OigsSI0PkmyftCRuAkOqOTx3%2BmF5cnT%2B%2B8FfPtKUR3KJ2DZ7rYf5ZzxHK2wHNqxqsSA7zIPM%2BQLe40gAqD%2BLZI5dCzj%2BROgAnDJ68VBBJFTbG1k1zePoW5PIBhcwocOSi%2FkC2Eg%2FxVlmomjBTEJwralxLWOmxd1z%2BhcUMt98z%2FdgrHX0XyoB6tlqt%2BROu1MIHrT7hWD%2BOVOsIpbdw38GGjrzBGG0xn5cvEvtG4Tz6pKrVwgsE2OPKV9y8AsG1vwt%2Fp9cIMbhIEoRwosCBMbObAIcIt6SVszUHc9AWmiwC3jLpcUB3Vxf0kxiH6IiY3ByIBOjiQsLK4IagZJatwJg3%2BE9gl3xew6ZIfHkXiiZxBDPolYs77l5JM0CJWYi4FAS6Miya1edjuUUeTITj7i4