;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6unbEdSX6nmwXSPKZFkzZIMxsMmsKlJdrmRBK1pBTX7XR%2B%2Bx5Ski0nzsQL75dAkchzz31f0t%2F3Aj5hWZieyIDvHe4dHNDR0RHdKCZiSiX5in1b4GEe013mOW6H5lKFwYPgc5q7I2%2FUHnVG%2FdFg5Dojd0A1ncqE3EHdoNzFQDvWOouSVMiY%2FBlAD8mhhCnpzwQLDaY79MilCVMjNmeL0SyLWKzLDx6xWEQs1CMtIz6fsbT80qaYpZniIxGnSsRa%2BKMHFma8%2FN4hP8TOlI9SkSQino4SiaVL5P4SGYtSDumjUC7RB6SzyYQrs28i%2FUzzYMnVoZino5hPWSoe%2BCiHGYV4XoLDElqKsPimrSHOmD8jtrKG0MToapHO8DwRIScYfPVZH1BqtGVBoBukOLwkYgiQyoIp3oQRWcTBXGi8T2c8t%2B8%2FNE2y2LcYr8iXUSI1tFgtwN444EDEK5FT0ymLAxbKmFOEMAhb9GXp5bOHL4aq2c6%2FJtxPsTE3tJxYhFVAtCzYa65TGmcLyowYs1HzqmKH9HGmRJTQLQ%2FhdU5XSv4O3Hz3L2fvz66Pb85OabygKY%2B5ggtbyaKMPh6IdM1M%2B%2FjYoBius2SMJYFksX6Nfa5So3IkFYJtaTGdr83NwZIkFFy36OMiaoVyGksFn9W%2BJ90GJcPuj7rFst4aOj%2FRydtXduWYpyx%2Fmyg5ZmMRihRExtKoHZjU%2BeQ0yP3conPmpxIyoWsOhQWJ8UGcNhAmxE1gSDWF584%2BzU%2BPL347%2BNtnGvNQzpEWZq%2F1MP%2BK53CB7cCGVS0WZAeZn%2Ba%2BgPc4cgfqT0KZYdcMjj8V2genlI6eKohcbDkDq6Z5HPyoE9ngAiZ0mHMxnQEbmas4gh1RNGMml7jWVLuREdPi%2FhX9GwqZb57jOTDWMnGulAD1dLFZsttyC8G9VrcQzL%2BmilXEsgf4z0BDZx4jjJbYz4vPq8ItwnlxxdUbBJaJseeULzl4BQNr%2Fib%2FTyYQ43AQJQjhWQECY6c2AQ4Rb3EzYuqepyAtNNj5vJmnxQHd3