counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6unbEdSX7F7maBNI9p0aQN0hTBoClcWqJtbiRRS8px3U7nt88hJdlyrdkKyIckikSee%2B6T9%2FLbQcBnbBmmZzLgB%2BODoyM6OTmhO8VETKkkX7GvazysYnpYeo7bo5VUYfAk%2BIpW7sSbdCe9yXAyooZOZUKjptn%2BEAPmVOtllKRCxuQvgDYmhxKmpL8QLDRg7sgjl2ZMTdiKrSeLZcRiXXzwiMUiYqGeaBnx1YKlxZcuxSxdKj4RcapErIU%2FeWLhkhffe%2BSH2JnySSqSRMTzSSKxdIM83CBjUcohfRLKDfqIIs7SCX7wJVFyGvLIqnPB%2FAWxrU5CE6ObdbrA80yEnGCv7Wd9RKnhzIJAt0hxGFnEXJNUFkzxNkzBIg4pQuN9uuCZlf6labaMfYvxgnwZJVJDh%2B0C7I0DDkS8Etqi6ZTFAQtlzCmCF8MOfd446eLps6FqtvMvCfdTbMzMJWcWYevPjgV7yXVK0%2BWalkaM2ah5WbExvV8oESV0z0P4jtONkv8Fbrb7t4u3F7endxfnNF3TnMdcwZCdZF0EDw9EumOmQ3xsUQwHWDLGkkCyWB9in6vUqBxJhZDZWExnazNzsCQJBdcder%2BOOqGcx1LBuY1vSb9Fyaj%2FvWmxrLdGzi909vqFXTnlKcveGiezqQhFCiJTadQOTOR%2FdFrkfurQJfNTCZnQNYPCgsT4IE5bpCVxExhSzeG5i4%2Br89Or34%2F%2B8YmmPJQrBLfZaz3Mv%2BA5XGM7sGFViwXZwdJPM19wE3qxhvpZgN%2FDp%2Bsbrl7BusbQJ%2FsqIqc6jmsVHZP3vUkEUMuhzf%2B3FHA0WFICPy5yEEhMbRSMYfS4HTH1yFOQEzrlsHc7i40jur%2B7oZnEPpgmZdDUl%2FET3JHZxoqghq%2Bk1m0f2I94D48r%2FsQhMyAePwkl4wjiWdiO5BM3j6SZr8RM%2BBxeATpC7S7L0TM5RbDMEByVWhYq9nIV8wwHqXaxD2m40Y1SJRPhI2YyIWM6jdhXrAgEnzL%2FMXN8Xh6Ih5acdSbbGAoFQpo80BthqDVLxWCkhzh%2FdZ456M6X3t96x%2FFy7nje8ZB1S3r2zoOszLJjegm2OsR7RDwMh5CEitrGh8%2FUFBo0%2Fhx0jnm7Szb